    <div class="inner">
        <h2 class="text-center">Contact Us</h2>
    </div>
    <section id="contact-us" class="col-md-12">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div id="spot-for-ad" class="col-md-2"></div>
            <div class="container col-md-8 margin-bottom-2">
                <h3 class="text-align-center">Feature Request</h3>
                <hr>
                <h4 class="text-indent-2">
                    Our website lives and evolves from the feedback we gain from the community. If there is something
                    you would like to see us add or modify please create a feature ticket. This will ask you some 
                    questions about what you would like to see us add to the website. Our team will then look at all 
                    of the requests and we may implement your exact feature request.
                </h4>
                <h4 class="text-indent-2">
                    <strong>Note:</strong> Before creating a new ticket, check to make sure there is not one 
                    already created with the same or similar idea.
                </h4>
                <br/>
                <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
                    <a href="https://github.com/Linesmerrill/police-cad/issues/new?assignees=&labels=&template=feature_request.md&title=" target="_blank">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-lg">Create Feature <i class="ion-android-arrow-forward"></i></button>
                </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="spot-for-ad" class="col-md-2"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div id="spot-for-ad" class="col-md-2"></div>
            <div class="container col-md-8 margin-bottom-2">
                <h3 class="text-align-center">Report a Bug</h3>
                <hr>
                <h4 class="text-indent-2">
                    If you have found something that seems to be out of place or not working correct, you can submit a 
                    bug ticket here. Our team treats these tickets as very high priority, so please make sure that you 
                    enter all the required details. This will help our team more quickly diagnose and fix the issue.
                </h4>
                <h4 class="text-indent-2">
                    <strong>Note:</strong> If more details are needed, out team may reach out to you directly for more 
                    information.
                </h4>
                <br/>
                <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
                    <a href="https://github.com/Linesmerrill/police-cad/issues/new?assignees=&labels=&template=bug_report.md&title=" target="_blank">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-lg">Report Bug <i class="ion-android-arrow-forward"></i></button>
                </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="spot-for-ad" class="col-md-2"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div id="spot-for-ad" class="col-md-2"></div>
            <div class="container col-md-8 margin-bottom-2">
                <h3 class="text-align-center">Reach out to Us</h3>
                <hr>
                <h4 class="text-indent-2">
                    Finally, if you would just like to provide our team with some words or encourgament or contact 
                    us for some other reason, you can either try our discord or send us an email. We will try to 
                    get back to you as soon as possible. Thank you! ❤️
                </h4>
                <br/>
                <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2 margin-bottom-2">
                    <a href="https://discord.gg/3ECFhqe" target="_blank">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-lg">Discord <i class="ion-android-arrow-forward"></i></button>
                </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <a href="mailto:support@linespolice-cad.com" target="_blank">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-lg">Email <i class="ion-android-arrow-forward"></i></button>
                </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="google-ad"></div>
    </section>
    
    <% include footer %>
